'''Burhakaba''' ({{lang-so|Buurhakaba}}) waa magaalo ku taal [[Bay, Somalia|Bay region]] ee [[Somalia]].

Magaalada waxaa loogu magac daray buur weyn oo ku taal bartamaha magaalada.

== Guudmarka ==
Burhakaba waa magaalada labaad ee ugu weyn gobolka Baay, waxaana lagu soo warramey inay ku nool yihiin dad gaaraya 360,795. <ref> [https://www.somalispot.com/threads/2014-unfpa-population-estimation-district-information-released.9350/ ] </ref> Waa 180km koonfur-galbeed caasimada [[Muqdisho]] iyo 60km waqooyi-bari u jirta xarunta gobolka [[Baydhabo]]. Degmada maamulka ee Buurhakaba waxay ka koobantahay ku dhowaad 400 tuulo. Magaalada waxaa lagu qiyaasaa in la degay lix qarni ka hor. <ref> [https://archive.is/20130212151205/http://www.xn--bevlkerungsstatistik-59b.de/wg.php?x=&men=gpro&lng = de & dat = 32 & geo = -198 & srt = npan & col = aohdq & pt = c & va = x & geo = 334102408 bevölkerungsstatistik.de] </ref> Burhakaba waxaa loo qaybiyaa dhowr tuulo maamul.

== Juqraafiga iyo cilmiga dadweynaha ==
Burhakaba waxay ku taalaa iskuduwaha 2.7991 ° N, 44.0794 ° E oo leh joog sare oo ah 196 mitir heerka badda. Ma lahan wabi joogto ah laakiin waxay leedahay dooxad weyn oo loo yaqaan "Bohol Wiinti" oo magaalada uga gudbeysa waqooyiga, bariga iyo koonfur-bari. Dooxadani waxay taageertaa wax-beerista aagga ay biyo-shubato ka dib roobabka xilliyeed. Magaalada waxaa lagu qiyaasaa in ay leedahay roobab sanadle ah oo gaaraya 550-620mm. Tirada dadka magaalada waxaa inta badan degta eelaay oo ah beel ka mid ah [[Rahanweyn]] waxaa kaloo daga Waalmuge. Luuqada ugu badan ee looga hadlo magaalada waa [[cushitic]] [[Maay language]]

In kasta oo aan si buuxda loo baarin, haddana Burhakaba waxaa la rumeysan yahay inay leedahay macdan aad u badan iyo dhagxaanta dhagaxa ah oo ay ku jiraan uranium (aagga Caliyow Geele), birta, aluminium, fosfooraska, kaolin, bauxite, granite, marble, dhagaxyada ciidda, dhagaxyada la jajabiyey, iyo dhagaxa nuuradda. Buurhakaba waxay leedahay istiraatiijiyad istiraatiijiyadeed oo ah inay isku xirto saddexda gobol ee kala ah Bakool, Hiiraan iyo shabeellada hoose

== Cimilada ==
Buurhakaba waxay leedahay j[[:en:Semi-arid_climate#Hot_semi-arid_climates|awi-kulul oomane ah (Köppen]] BSh), sida inta badan koonfurta Soomaaliya. Celceliska celceliska heerkulka waa 26.2 ° C ama 79.2 ° F, laakiin heerkulku wuxuu gaari karaa illaa 43 illaa 45 ° C (109.4 ilaa 113.0 ° F) Disember iyo Janaayo. Taa bedelkeeda, magaalooyinka ku yaal qaybta woqooyi ee dalka guud ahaan waxay leeyihiin [[:en:Desert_climate#Hot_desert_climates|cimilo kulul oo qalalan]] (Köppen BWh).

